de: Amendment No.1 to the Administration Agreement between the Government of Switzerland, represented by seco, the IBRD and IDA concerning the South Africa Financial Sector Development and Reform Program Multi-Donor Trust Fund (TF 072243)  - 15-03-2016 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, IBRD und IDA betreffend des Multi-Geber Treuhandfonds der Finanzierung des Programs zur Entwicklung und Reform des Finanzsektors in Südafrika
en: Amendment No.1 to the Administration Agreement between the Government of Switzerland, represented by seco, the IBRD and IDA concerning the South Africa Financial Sector Development and Reform Program Multi-Donor Trust Fund (TF 072243)  - 15-03-2016 - Administration Agreement between the Government of Switzerland, represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs and the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Development Association concerning the South Africa Financial Sector Development and Reform Program Multi-Donor Trust Fund (TF 072243)
fr: Amendment No.1 to the Administration Agreement between the Government of Switzerland, represented by seco, the IBRD and IDA concerning the South Africa Financial Sector Development and Reform Program Multi-Donor Trust Fund (TF 072243)  - 15-03-2016 - Accord entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO, la BIRD et l'IDA concernant le fonds fiduciaire multidonateur sur le financement du project pour la réforme du secteur financier de la République de l'Afrique du Sud
